HCRTOS SDK License Notice

This repository is a redistributable SDK staging tree used by UniFrog. It is
not licensed as a single permissive work.

The repository contains several classes of material:

- UniFrog-specific build glue, file lists, integration notes, and small
  compatibility edits contributed by UniFrog contributors.
- Open-source third-party components such as FatFs, FreeRTOS-derived code,
  NuttX-derived code, Newlib headers, zlib interfaces, and Linux-style public
  headers. These remain under their original upstream licenses.
- Vendor HCRTOS/SF2000 headers, binary archives, and source fragments whose
  redistribution terms are not equivalent to MIT/BSD/Apache.

